      "description": "# üèéÔ∏è Welcome to the Racing Lab!\n\nWelcome to our Formula 1 Terraform lab! Just like a race car is built from many precisely engineered components, our infrastructure is defined using **Infrastructure as Code** with Terraform.\n\n**What you'll learn:**\n- How Terraform manages infrastructure\n- Okta provider configuration\n- Racing team resource definitions\n- F1-themed practical examples\n\n**First, we need to set up your Okta credentials!** Let's get you connected to your racing command center! üèÅ"
