      "description": "üèÜ Provider Requirements\n\nThe `required_providers` block declares which tire manufacturer we'll use for the race!\n\n**Key Points:**\n- **source**: Where to download the provider (like a parts supplier)\n- **version**: Which version to use (like tire compound specifications)\n\n**Understanding Provider Sources:**\nWhen you see `source = \"okta/okta\"`, this means:\n- The provider comes from the **Okta namespace** in the HashiCorp Registry.  You can see what's published in the Okta namespace at https://registry.terraform.io/namespaces/okta \n- This provider's docs are online at https://registry.terraform.io/providers/okta/okta/latest/docs. When you see \"providers/okta/okta\" in the URL, you know you're reading the docs for the same provider that you imported here. \n\nüí° **Pro Tip**: The provider docs are your best friend! They show:\n- Current and past versions available\n- All available resources and data sources\n- Configuration examples and guides\n\n"
    },
